bugs.cf_release_notes:
In Red Hat Enterprise Linux 7.0 Beta, the "named" PID file has been moved from the BIND default location /var/run/named/named.pid to the new location /run/named/named.pid. In addition, the "session-key" file has been moved to /run/named/session.key. These locations need to be specified by statements in the "options" section of the BIND configuration:

options {
    ...
    pid-file          "/run/named/named.pid";
    session-keyfile   "/run/named/session.key";
    ...
};
